        <h2>Simplify and reduce the cost of your customer’s network</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-40">AT&amp;T FlexWare uses Network Function Virtualization (NFV) technology so you no longer have to buy, manage, and maintain a stack of specialized network appliances like routers and firewalls. Instead customers simply run these, and virtually any other network function, as software on a FlexWare device.</p>
       
